359
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,260
White Hair?

360
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:34,630
Yan Fengshan died for you.

361
00:39:35,970 --> 00:39:37,820
And Cen Pickles risked everything for you.

362
00:39:40,040 --> 00:39:41,950
