363
00:39:58,550 --> 00:40:00,170
They did not risk their lives for me.

364
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:06,170
They only wished

365
00:40:06,170 --> 00:40:08,380
to protect the grain and flour of Chang'an.

366
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,050
You asked me what I lived for.

367
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,490
I live

368
