I spent years planning

374
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:04,650
before returning to Chang'an

375
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:10,010
to destroy the entire Huben Army,

376
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:16,700
yet I failed to realize

377
00:41:19,130 --> 00:41:20,690
I was one of them.

378
00:41:23,610 --> 00:41:24,720
My father

379
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:28,340
raised the Huben Army for Chang'an.

380
00:41:29,170 --> 00:41:30,340
Every member is a shadow guard.

381
00:41:32,250 --> 00:41:33,390
So many died

382
00:41:33,390 --> 00:41:35,130
without leaving their names behind.

383
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:39,650
That is the price of protection.

384
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,170
For a Huben guard,

385
00:41:44,850 --> 00:41:46,170
to kill the enemy

386
00:41:47,110 --> 00:41:48,650
is the highest merit.

387
00:41:49,430 --> 00:41:50,530
You think

388
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,820
you can win?

389
00:41:58,470 --> 00:42:00,780
The shadow guards you hid in the city

390
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:02,930
all believe you are trapped

391
00:42:02,930 --> 00:42:04,860
in the granary of Hidden Soldier Alley.

392
00:42:06,510 --> 00:42:07,940
The remnants of the Baiwenhu Army

393
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,700
and the forces of the four regional commanders

394
00:42:12,590 --> 00:42:14,820
have already united.

395
00:42:16,240 --> 00:42:17,940
The entire heartland of our empire

396
00:42:19,590 --> 00:42:21,740
has become a trap for your Tiemo army.

397
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:24,780
Do you think

398
00:42:26,010 --> 00:42:27,260
you can win?

399
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,870
As long as I live,

400
00:42:31,950 --> 00:42:33,490
the victor is not yet decided.

401
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:42,090
White Hair,

402
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:45,050
you

403
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:50,380
forced yourself here on sheer will alone.

404
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,860
How do you plan to kill me?

405
00:42:57,390 --> 00:42:59,490
Can your hands, meant for writing and pouring tea,

406
00:43:00,590 --> 00:43:01,970
even lift a sword?

407
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:07,050
Can the words

408
00:43:08,130 --> 00:43:09,740
"protect Chang'an" kill me?

409
00:43:11,990 --> 00:43:12,490
No.

410
00:43:13,990 --> 00:43:15,570
But another phrase can.

411
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:22,220
Fifteen years ago, in the Grand Academy,

412
00:43:23,840 --> 00:43:26,010
when you taught us to make funnel timers,

413
00:43:27,510 --> 00:43:28,820
you said six words.

414
00:44:22,550 --> 00:44:24,220
The room is full of flour dust.

415
00:44:25,110 --> 00:44:26,740
You should "settle the dust to prevent fire."

416
00:44:27,990 --> 00:44:28,860
Remember?

417
00:44:29,240 --> 00:44:30,480
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

418
00:44:40,030 --> 00:44:41,610
With a broken body,

419
00:44:42,910 --> 00:44:44,820
I kill the King of Tiemo.

420
00:44:45,430 --> 00:44:46,300
Today,

421
00:44:46,910 --> 00:44:48,090
